The paper deals with video captioning, which is a task related to computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new visual feature encoding technique using Gated Recurrent Units (GRUs), which falls under the category of machine learning and deep learning. Hence, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. Additionally, the paper deals with video processing, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a new state-of-the-art method for video captioning, which involves designing a language model, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
